{
  "stem": "15694.9",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "From then on, we were both looking every day after work, going around looking, hoping, to find friends or somebody we know who could help us either with work, or with food, or with something.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And as weeks went by, we were given other-- we were given proper barracks afterwards.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "As weeks went by, we had hard work and not enough food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We could see that we were losing strength, losing weight.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We also heard for the first time the word 'muselmann.' Now, muselmann actually got a new meaning there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The actual word of muselmann means like a-- a-- like a-- Mohammedan priest, sort of priest.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there are some who, because of the fanaticism, sort of don't eat and get very thin.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I'm not quite sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Somebody called that word, and it stuck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Like for instance, Kanada Kommand, the people who worked-- worked, received a transport, and had everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "People brought along food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You name it, they had it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And it was probably Canada in the thought that it's a country where everything is still available.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Somebody coined it, and so it was called Kanada Kommand, Kommando.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we saw for the first time these so-called muselmann were skeletal figures, very thin already, and on the way out, almost too far gone to ever recover.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Some of them even if they did get food, they wouldn't.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And in most cases, these people either dropped.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Or if there was a selection, they would have been taken away to a place of recuperation-- the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Now, I said to my father, if we don't have any change in our situation, we will soon be one of them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And then my father, luckily, met somebody who he knew from Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Name is Tiba.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
